race.comment: CAITLIN (5) was heavily supported when at the races for the first time and didn't let backers down with a solid win around this circuit. Winning hoop Lenton sticks in the saddle and again gets the benefit of her 2kg claim. Can go back-to-back without surprising. CEEKAY'S CHOICE (2) is a consistent commodity who has remarkably never missed the top-five in 13 career outings to date. High on confidence following a last-start victory and has to be included in calculations. WARILLA GORILLA (1) has placed two of three over this six-furlong journey and is usually thereabouts. Top-three credentials. AZUKI (6) has placed three from four at this track and will strip fitter second-up from the break. In the mix. MOONFLEET (3) best of the rest while fresh.
